  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/88a179fef84dc23363422f4214e3d980.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" width=520 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/88a179fef84dc23363422f4214e3d980.webm?t=1725095396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/88a179fef84dc23363422f4214e3d980.mp4?t=1725095396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/f61558095463b7417949a853f4f06adc.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/f61558095463b7417949a853f4f06adc.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span>Game Overview<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/f61558095463b7417949a853f4f06adc.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/f61558095463b7417949a853f4f06adc.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span></h2>Break down gems by sorting them pair by pair, or set up <strong>non matching</strong> gems to try and maximizes how many you can break at once!This game encourages <strong>high scoring combos</strong> over simple brick matching, so creativity and combos are king!<br><br>A part of the <strong>Game Buddy</strong> series that faithfully recreates the look, sounds, and feel of classic late 80's handheld games in a way that's like experiencing an alternate timeline of gaming history.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/5e5fbd5fc8933b2fb27649b02781f504.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/5e5fbd5fc8933b2fb27649b02781f504.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span>Gameplay<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/5e5fbd5fc8933b2fb27649b02781f504.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/5e5fbd5fc8933b2fb27649b02781f504.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span></h2>Drop like blocks on one another to make them disappear...<strong>But</strong>! Don't do it too simply, or you'll incur a block penalty! Avoid the penalty and get the most points by dropping gems in a way they'll chain off each into an avalanche of gems and points!<br><br>Two becomes four, four becomes eight...<br><strong>how high of a combo can you make?</strong><br><br><strong>GAME-A</strong><br>Use endurance and imagination in this mode to seeing how long you can keep stacking and how big of a combo chain you can make! All scores are accumulated and can be used to unlock a wide variety of new types of blocks.<br><br><strong>GAME-B</strong><br>Start with a set number of blocks, and try to destroy them all before your screen becomes overrun! Adjust the stage and/or difficulty of either mode for added challenge!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span>Features<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>puzzle game-play that encourages quick foresightful thinking.<br></li><li>8-bit sights and sounds that faithfully emulates the early era of handheld gaming.<br></li><li>Six different types of block skins to unlock.<br></li><li>two game modes, four difficulty levels, and five stages to choose from.<br></li><li>Catchy and nostalgic chiptune music.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to access the menu</h2><strong>To access the game menu and manual, press select button on gamepad or shift key on keyboard.</strong>",
