24 /></picture></span>Features<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.apng?t=1725095396\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729390/extras/c5b2d416b205f8245cecd03ba2a50da9.poster.avif?t=1725095396\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>puzzle game-play that encourages quick foresightful thinking.<br></li><li>8-bit sights and sounds that faithfully emulates the early era of handheld gaming.<br></li><li>Six different types of block skins to unlock.<br></li><li>two game modes, four difficulty levels, and five stages to choose from.<br></li><li>Catchy and nostalgic chiptune music.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to access the menu</h2><strong>To access the game menu and manual, press select button on gamepad or shift key on keyboard.</strong>",
